Why emails fail on PythonAnywhere 🔍
PythonAnywhere's free accounts block outbound SMTP ports (587/465). Your current Gmail SMTP setup hits this wall silently (fail_silently=True hides the error). Brevo's API works over HTTPS (port 443) which PythonAnywhere always allows — that's exactly why it's the right choice here.

